To-Do list App

#General steps to follow when creating a project

-Thinking about the UI

-Create the UI

-Functionality
 -Add a TODO
 -Delete a TODO
 -Mark a TODO as complete
 -Total items count

-Data
 -tasks - an array
 -task -{done, text, id}

-Functions (in code)
 -addTodo
 -deleteTodo
 -checkTodo
 -renderTodo
 -showNotification